{
  "texts": [
    "This decentralization ensures that even if a certain data source fails or goes offline, datasets from other sources remain accessible, improving the overall system's reliability.",
    "ImplementationTo implement a prototype of our proposed framework [47], we use Hyperledger Fabric [48] to create a permissioned blockchain network.",
    "The blockchain network consists of two business domains, namely, the Sales and Marketing domains.",
    "Each domain in the Hyperledger Fabric network has a Membership Service Provider (MSP) that uses public key infrastructure (PKI) to manage identities and authentication.",
    "We used the Hyperledger Fabric cryptogen utility tool to generate public and private keys for all entities in the network."
  ]
}